707049f-a.title: Brooklyn: Throop Ave. - Halsey St.
707049f-a.text:
Throop Avenue, south from halsey Street, showing the east side
of the avenue. At Macon Street is the Roman Catholic 2-hurch
of Cur Lady of ictory.
P. L. 'berr  August 26, 1941
